Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.11,0:00:08.32,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Tonight is Kanie and my first class reunion since graduating high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:14.28,Signs,,0,0,0,,Graduating Class of 1989, ***** Academy Class Reunion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:13.05,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,That so? Kanie {\i1}does{\i0} seem different somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.05,0:00:14.61,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,It took me off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:15.72,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Right, Hana?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:18.36,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:21.50,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,This girl was so rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.11,0:00:26.14,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,She didn't remember me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:28.43,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I-I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.43,0:00:31.08,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I recognized her on sight, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.69,0:00:40.72,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I-It's because he recognized me on sight that I went though all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:46.94,Signs,,0,0,0,,The 25 Year Old High School Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:46.94,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(82,675)}Episode 4: On the Night of the Class Reunion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:54.26,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is so embarrassing. Why does Kanie have follow me around?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.69,0:00:55.32,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.75,0:00:56.46,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,My feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:00:59.25,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Are you still having cramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.25,0:01:01.20,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. They're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:05.16,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I see. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.95,0:01:06.62,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.47,0:01:10.54,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be that he was worried about me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:12.05,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.49,0:01:13.92,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Kanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.49,0:01:17.26,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,If you act strangely, people will suspect something's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:18.75,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:21.42,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That can't be right—this guy's just the worst.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:26.65,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,B-But Kanie, if we're together like this, \Npeople will {\i1}know{\i0} something's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.65,0:01:28.02,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,This is no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.13,0:01:31.76,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,W-Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:39.95,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Wait, Kanie! Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:42.02,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:46.41,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Today you aren't a student, so I won't stop halfway. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:49.64,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Plea—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.15,0:01:54.46,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Man, everyone's changed too much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:57.15,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I couldn't even recognize any of the girls.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:59.43,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way, someone's coming in?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:04.28,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,K-Kanie, you can't. We'll be found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:09.94,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,If you make any noise, we might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.33,0:02:15.80,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Oh yeah, that guy Kanie was with Natori. Were they ever close?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.17,0:02:18.55,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're dating, surprisingly enough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:19.74,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For real?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:23.99,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I guess that's what it looks like, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:25.89,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}N-No way...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:30.25,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}That's right, Kanie had a crush on Natori back then, didn't he?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:32.60,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}W-What did he just say?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:35.70,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kanie had a crush on {\i0}me{\i1}?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:42.88,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That time, Kanie was especially intense{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:46.36,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as if he were trying to distract me from what I had just heard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.15,0:02:48.66,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? No way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:50.77,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, that's...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:56.74,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}We can't, not in a place like this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:03:00.70,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Why is this happening? I can't keep quiet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:02.82,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,K-Kanie—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:09.92,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-It's so deep!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:14.92,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Hold on to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:19.66,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,No, K-Kanie... No more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:32.80,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You can finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:54.84,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I-I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:59.95,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,People might be suspicious after we were gone for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:01.84,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,S-Say, Kanie...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:02.84,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:07.48,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,About, umm... what they were saying back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:08.44,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.85,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,N-Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:17.80,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry! Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:21.24,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'll make up a suitable excuse, so take it easy and come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:27.24,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can never understand what Kanie is thinking.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:43.80,Songs,,0,0,0,,Who could have predicted this reunion?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:51.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,I reel in this thread of memory, and use it to spin my tale
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:56.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,Why are you all pushy one minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:05:02.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,and then gentle the next?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:07.74,Songs,,0,0,0,,As long as the two of us share this secret
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:13.30,Songs,,0,0,0,,it will be the light that guides you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:18.08,Songs,,0,0,0,,to somewhere in the yet-unknowable future
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:22.52,Songs,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, it's okay to optimistic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:26.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,I want to know everything about you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:32.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,hidden deep within those eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:37.26,Songs,,0,0,0,,I can't control these feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:44.42,Songs,,0,0,0,,Piece by piece, my heart is being snatched away
